{"id":94,"count":1,"description":"Heart of India \u2013 Madhya Pradesh \ud83c\udfde\ufe0f\r\nKnown as the Heart of India, Madhya Pradesh is a land where history, culture, and nature come alive. From the magnificent Khajuraho temples with their intricate carvings and the spiritual aura of Ujjain and Omkareshwar to the majestic Gwalior and Orchha forts, MP is steeped in heritage. Nature lovers can explore the famous wildlife sanctuaries of Kanha, Bandhavgarh, and Pench, home to the Royal Bengal Tiger. The state also boasts ancient caves at Bhimbetka, the stupas of Sanchi, and tranquil river ghats. With its unique mix of spirituality, architecture, wildlife, and tribal traditions, Madhya Pradesh offers an authentic Indian experience at the very heart of the country.","link":"https:\/\/realtrips.thefuturecity.in\/destinations\/heart-of-india-madhyapradesh\/","name":"HEART OF INDIA MADHYAPRADESH","slug":"heart-of-india-madhyapradesh","taxonomy":"destination","parent":0,"meta":[],"thumbnail":{"width":900,"height":596,"file":"2025\/09\/MADHYAPRADESH.png","filesize":919989,"sizes":{"medium":{"file":"MADHYAPRADESH-300x199.png","width":300,"height":199,"filesize":43654,"mime_type":"image\/png","source_url":"https:\/\/realtrips.thefuturecity.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/MADHYAPRADESH-300x199.png"},"thumbnail":{"file":"MADHYAPRADESH-150x150.png","width":150,"height":150,"filesize":17988,"mime_type":"image\/png","source_url":"https:\/\/realtrips.thefuturecity.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/MADHYAPRADESH-150x150.png"},"medium_large":{"file":"MADHYAPRADESH-768x509.png","width":768,"height":509,"filesize":501353,"mime_type":"image\/png","source_url":"https:\/\/realtrips.thefuturecity.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/MADHYAPRADESH-768x509.png"},"trip-thumb-size":{"file":"MADHYAPRADESH-374x226.png","width":374,"height":226,"filesize":129292,"mime_type":"image\/png","source_url":"https:\/\/realtrips.thefuturecity.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/MADHYAPRADESH-374x226.png